<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .grade {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        .content {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Assignment Feedback Report</h2>
        <p><strong>Student:</strong> {{ student_name }}</p>
        <p><strong>Assignment:</strong> {{ assignment_name }}</p>
        <p class="grade">Overall Grade: {{ grade }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <p>{{ student_name }},</p>

        <p>Hello from the AI Krew. Your graded assignment is attached to this email. Please review the detailed feedback in the PDF document.</p>

        <p>The report includes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Overall score and summary</li>
            <li>Detailed criteria breakdown with examples from your work</li>
            <li>Specific advice for improvement</li>
            <li>Your complete submitted text</li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you have any questions about the feedback, please don't hesitate to reach out during office hours or via email.</p>

        <p>Keep up the great work!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from {{ from_name }}. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
